title: Paper Production, All Grades for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1918-1942 (2)--Original Data, 1942-1964. Source: Ftc; Data For 1918-1920: Monthly Statistical Summary Of The Paper Industry. Data For 1921-1942: Survey Of Current Business.
